  9→//! Fundus scenario tests for remote dispatch via SSH.
 10→//!
 11→//! Localhost tests run on every `cargo test` — requires jjfu_* accounts
 12→//! provisioned on localhost (see JJSTF-test-fundus.adoc).
 13→//!
 14→//! Cerebro tests use `#[ignore]` — run via tabtarget or `--ignored`.
 15→//!
 16→//! Relay tests mint real pensa (creating git commits). This is intentional —
 17→//! these are end-to-end scenario tests.
 18→
 19→use std::path::PathBuf;
 20→
